FBIS3-53949 "drnes014_n_94010" FBIS-NES-94-014 Document Type:Daily Report 21 Jan 1994 LEBANON Parliament Mourns Death of Syrian President's Son NC2101123494 Shanayh Voice of the Mountain in Arabic 1218 GMT 21 Jan 94 NC2101123494 Shanayh Voice of the Mountain Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Unscheduled report] [Text] Ladies and gentlemen, we were told a few moments ago that Basil al-Asad, son of Syrian Arab leader Hafiz al-Asad, has been martyred in a regrettable road accident. The Lebanese Chamber of Deputies is mourning his death and has announced the postponement of its session and a five-day mourning period. [Paris AFP in English at 1215 GMT on 21 Janaury adds: "The accident happened on the road to Damascus Airport."]
